阶级关系有什么新的变化","box":[[174,2715],[1964,2734],[1964,2775],[174,2756]]},{"text":"1975年第5期","box":[[173,2833],[466,2839],[465,2875],[173,2869]]},{"text":"（总391）·5","box":[[1654,2850],[1956,2853],[1956,2889],[1654,2886]]}],"dimensions":{"height":3317,"width":2638}}